    <item>
      <title>Hardware Architecture</title>
      <link>https://iams1am.github.io/bracu-alter-site/platforms/rover/alter-rover-v1/hardware/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://iams1am.github.io/bracu-alter-site/platforms/rover/alter-rover-v1/hardware/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;chassis--mobility&#34;&gt;Chassis &amp;amp; Mobility&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Modular aluminum frame with reinforced mounts&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;All-terrain wheel system optimized for rubble and uneven surfaces&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Suspension designed for stability during obstacle traversal&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;sensors&#34;&gt;Sensors&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;2D/3D LiDAR for mapping and obstacle detection&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Depth &amp;amp; RGB cameras for perception&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;IMU and wheel encoders for state estimation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;compute--power&#34;&gt;Compute &amp;amp; Power&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Embedded compute unit for autonomy and perception&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Distributed microcontroller system for motor and sensor control&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Power-efficient battery management system for extended missions&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
    </item>
